data.title: Jyamire, Khotang
data.meta_description: Jyamire is a village and Village Development Committee in Khotang District in the Sagarmatha Zone of eastern Nepal. At the time of the 1991 Nepal census it had a population of 1,579 persons living in 298 individual households.
data.text:
Jyamire is a village and Village Development Committee in Khotang District in the Sagarmatha Zone of eastern Nepal. At the time of the 1991 Nepal census it had a population of 1,579 persons living in 298 individual households.[1]
